Description: This package provides a simple R interface to the database tables used in the Milestones Project,
  <https://datavis.ca/milestones/>,
  reflecting the history of data visualization, as used in datavis.ca/milestones.
  Functions are provided to retrieve the tables of milestones events, authors, references, etc.
